  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK173">
<l>ciṟṟiṉpam veḵki yaṟaṉalla ceyyārē</l>
<l>maṟṟiṉpam vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who desire the higher pleasures (of heaven) will not act unjustly through desire of the trifling joy. (in this life.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
